tilizadas</strong></h2>
<ul>
<li><p>Java 8 (main lang)</p></li>
<li><p>JUnit (unit test)</p></li>
<li>Vavr (functional)</li>
<li>Lombok (code generator)</li>
<li><p>Spring Boot (framework)</p></li>
<li>Undertow (embedded application server)</li>
<li>Netflix Feing (http clients<span style=3D"font-size: 16.0px;">)</span><=
/li>
<li>Kafka (broker)</li>
<li>Flyway (db evolutions)</li>
<li>PostgreSQL (write/read database)</li>
<li>Graylog (log system)</li>
</ul>
